      <div class="msgContentFrame">Hello there. I am new to these forums, and a friend of mine told me this is the place to go if you're interested in FF14. Sorry if this thread is not in the right section. <br /> <br />Due to overwhelming negative reviews I did not wish to buy the game, however, after viewing the future patchnotes my interest came back. I am just asking if anyone would be so kind to give me a buddy pass to experience the game, or direct me as to where i might find a place that gives out FF14 passes. I promise i will become an active participant in these forums and post my opinions and what not on the game for as long as the pass lasts, and may in turn buy it if i enjoyed my time with the game. <br /> <br />Once again i apologize if these sorts of threads aren't allowed in general, i just don't really have any friends that would be interested in such a game, let alone ones that would have bought the collector's edition. Also sorry about the name, my usual internet alias was taken. </div>
