      <div class="msgContentFrame">Getting a buddy pass is like having a full retail version of the game.  You don't need to go out and buy it, because of that reason.  Not saying that someone isn't generous and will give one out.  Good luck with trying to track one down.  Your best bet is go out and buy one, or by chance you have a ps3... wait until the beta comes out for it and try it then.  If you like it then you should have to buy it like 99% of us did for the PC version<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Time is but a window <br />Death is but a doorway <br />I'll be back!!!! <br /> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1772013.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
