      <div class="msgContentFrame">Yeah, the CE comes with the buddy pass. I think you're going to find it rather difficult to get a buddy pass. Not because nobody is willing to share, but because they most likely have been already used. I gave mine to my room mate. I expected him to only be able to play for 30 days, but that's not the case. He is still playing, so what SillyHawk says is true. You have to put in your credit card information to be able to play with the buddy pass. Which means my friend will be a paying member just like me after they stop with the free trials. Makes me feel better about my purchase. Because I was rather disappointed to find out that us Americans don't get the cloth map like other people. I really wanted that, could care less about the silly tumbler. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/557565.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
